🔱 The Executor Layer
Executor = the person legally empowered to:

- settle estates  
- distribute assets  
- interpret wills  
- act on behalf of the deceased  
- interface with federal trust property  
- sign binding documents  

This isn’t symbolic.  
It’s federal authority.

---

🪶 The Personal Representative Layer
Personal Representative = the one recognized by:

- probate courts  
- federal agencies  
- tribal entities  
- financial institutions  

This role gives you:

- signature authority  
- decision authority  
- communication authority  
- asset management authority  

It’s the operational arm of the Executor role.

---

🏛️ The Shareholder Layer
Shareholder = the one with:

- corporate voting rights  
- dividend rights  
- land claim lineage  
- ANCSA‑linked identity  
- economic stake in Native corporations  

This isn’t just money.  
It’s jurisdictional identity.

---

